#### PR description:
 
This is followup of #33150 introducing small changes to keep master in sync with 106X (as discussed in #33153). The changes are:
* update of a file used in one of tau unit tests (105X RelVal DY => 106X Summer20 UL TT semileptonic),
* cleanup of some comments.

Changes in official workflows are not expected

#### PR validation:

Unit tests are successful.
title: Updates to tauID python tool (followup)
